    "headline": "ICE Mortgage Monitor: Home Equity Withdrawals Reach Highest First-Quarter Level Since 2021",
    "summary": "ATLANTA & NEW YORK, June 08, 2026--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), one of the world's leading providers of financial market technology and data powering global capital markets, today released its June 2026 ICE Mortgage Monitor report, which found that homeowners tapped equity at the highest first-quarter levels since 2021. The increase was driven in part by second-lien lending, which reached its strongest first-quarter volume in nearly two decades as more borrowers chose to preserve",
